INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('7', 'Django Rest Framework框架初步介绍', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">使用Django Rest Framework之前我们要先知道，它是什么，能干什么用？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　引用官方一句话：Django REST框架是用于构建Web API的功能强大且灵活的工具包。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　那为什么要使用Rest Framework？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　Django REST Framework可以在Django的基础上迅速实现API，并且自身还带有WEB的测试页面，可以方便的测试自己的API。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">web应用模式分两种：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1. 前后端不分离</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 在前后端不分离的引用模式中，前端页面看到的效果都是由后端控制的，由后端页面渲染或者重定向，也就是后端需要控制前端的展示，前端与后端的耦合度很高，这种模式比较适合纯网页应用，但是后端对接APP时，App可能并不需要后端返回一个HTML网页,二仅仅是数据本身,所以后端原本返回网页的接口不在适用前端APP应用,为了对接APP后端嗨需再开发一套接口。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 这个可以看我之前写的DJango博客就可以知道，每次返回时都是使用render 或者redirect来返回的，需要带上HTML页面和参数</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2. 前后端分离</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 在前后端分离的应用模式中，后端仅返回前端所需要的数据，不再渲染HTML页面，不再控制前端的效果，只要前端用户看到什么效果，从后端请求的数据如何加载到前端中，都由前端自己决定，网页有网页自己的处理方式，APP有APP的处理方式，但无论哪种前端所需要的数据基本相同，后端仅需开发一套逻辑对外提供数据即可，在前后端分离的应用模式中,前端与后端的耦合度相对较低</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;在前后端分离的应用模式中,我们通常将后端开发的每一视图都成为一个接口,或者API,前端通过访问接口来对数据进行增删改查</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果项目的需求是后一种情况的话，那么就可以用到Django Rest Framework了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">感兴趣的可以参考官方资料：<a href=\"https://www.django-rest-framework.org/\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s;\">https://www.django-rest-framework.org/</a>，如果看不懂英文的伙伴，可以参考rest的中文文档：<a href=\"http://www.iamnancy.top/djangorestframework/Home/\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(6, 129, 186); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s;\">http://www.iamnancy.top/djangorestframework/Home/</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.打开pycharm编辑器，新建项目，选择如下：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://img2020.cnblogs.com/blog/782587/202003/782587-20200322233956144-1812541540.png\" alt=\"\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: auto; padding: 0px; box-shadow: rgb(221, 221, 221) 0px 0px 3px; font-size: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;这里虚拟环境是django_rest，如果看不懂，可以参考我前面写的<a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/liudinglong/p/12538579.html\" target=\"_blank\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(6, 129, 186); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s;\">虚拟环境使用</a>的文章。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.建好之后的项目结构如下：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://img2020.cnblogs.com/blog/782587/202003/782587-20200322234014755-1053007828.png\" alt=\"\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: auto; padding: 0px; box-shadow: rgb(221, 221, 221) 0px 0px 3px; font-size: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;在创建的虚拟环境中安装Django&nbsp;REST&nbsp;framework：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://img2020.cnblogs.com/blog/782587/202003/782587-20200322234103277-639296279.png\" alt=\"\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: auto; padding: 0px; box-shadow: rgb(221, 221, 221) 0px 0px 3px; font-size: 0px;\"/></p><h2 id=\"auto-id-3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, 黑体, Arial; font-weight: 500; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(235, 235, 235); margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 18px; padding: 4px 4px 4px 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; white-space: normal; background: rgb(0, 204, 255); border-radius: 6px; box-shadow: rgb(95, 90, 75) 0px 0px 0px 1px, rgba(10, 10, 0, 0.5) 1px 1px 6px 1px; height: 25px; text-shadow: rgb(34, 34, 34) 2px 2px 3px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><em id=\"locator-auto-id-3\" class=\"lnh-article-header-locator\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: fixed; display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 0px; font-size: 0px;\"></em>　　开发步骤</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　上面已经安装好环境和包，现在就开始开发了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; text-indent: 30px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 850.141px; font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.首先配置setting文件，加入rest_framework应用。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; trans